/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;!-- LONG TAIL KEYWORDS --&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;h2&gt;What are Long-Tail Keywords?&lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xD;&#xA;Long-tail keywords are longer and more specific search phrases. They have low competition and higher chances to rank.&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
